Gone fishing

phase 1 build:
-user clicks anywhere within designated screen area
-if clicks within the correct zone a fish will be collected, and points
will be added based on fish type
-game over if a shark is caught
-win if all fish are caught and shark is avoided

phase 2 build:
-fish heads will pop out of random areas, user must click heads before
disappearing
-shark fin will randomly pop up, is clicked game over
-win if all fish are collected

phase 3 build:
-easy, med, hard lvls
-fish will pop up faster depending the harder the setting
-shark fins will pop out more the harder it gets
-shark fin will randomly pop up, if clicked game over
-win if all fish are collected